A. Installation

	A.1	Tools install
		$ cd ~/temp/DRIVER_PACKAGE/tools/PLATFORM
		$ sudo cp * /usr/sbin

	A.2	Tools uninstall
		$ sudo rm /usr/sbin/sdc-config
		$ sudo rm /usr/sbin/sdc-uart-cfg

	A.3 Script install
		Please finish driver installation describe in README_Driver file
		(need apply patch RHEL_x.x.patch) and A.1 Tools install section
		before doing instruction below.

		$ cd ~/temp/DRIVER_PACKAGE/script/RHEL
		$ sudo cp sdc-start.sh /usr/local/bin/
		$ sudo cp sdc-stop.sh /usr/local/bin/
		$ sudo cp sdc-board-cfg.service /etc/systemd/system/
		$ sudo systemctl enable sdc-board-cfg
		$ sudo systemctl start sdc-board-cfg
		$ sudo sdc-uart-cfg -s

	A.4 Script uninstall
		Please finish driver uninstallation describe in README_Driver file
		and A.2 Tools uninstall section before doing instruction below.

		$ sudo systemctl stop sdc-board-cfg
		$ sudo systemctl disable sdc-board-cfg
		$ sudo rm /usr/local/bin/sdc-start.sh
		$ sudo rm /usr/local/bin/sdc-stop.sh
		$ sudo rm /etc/systemd/system/sdc-board-cfg.service
		$ sudo rm -Rf /usr/share/sdc_8250/
		$ reboot

